---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="oto - Push-to-Talk Voice Transcription App">
	<div class="navbar bg-base-100 shadow-lg">
		<div class="flex-1">
			<a class="btn btn-ghost text-xl">üéôÔ∏è oto</a>
		</div>
		<div class="flex-none gap-2">
			<a href="#features" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Features</a>
			<a href="#installation" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Installation</a>
			<a href="#usage" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Usage</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Download</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-100">
		<div class="hero-content text-center">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<div class="badge badge-primary mb-4">v1.0.0</div>
				<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Push-to-Talk Voice Transcription</h1>
				<p class="py-6 text-lg">WPF System Tray application that records voice using a hotkey and transcribes it using OpenAI's Audio Transcriptions API, then pastes the text into the focused application.</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
						Download for Windows
					</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
						View on GitHub
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="features" class="py-20 bg-base-200">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Features</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">‚å®Ô∏è</span>
							Hold-to-Talk
						</h3>
						<p>Hold Ctrl+Alt+Space to record, release to transcribe. Simple and intuitive.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">ü§ñ</span>
							OpenAI Integration
						</h3>
						<p>Uses gpt-4o-mini-transcribe (default) or whisper-1 for accurate transcriptions.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">üìã</span>
							Auto Paste
						</h3>
						<p>Automatically pastes transcribed text via Ctrl+V into your active application.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">üîí</span>
							Secure Storage
						</h3>
						<p>API keys are encrypted using Windows DPAPI for maximum security.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">üîî</span>
							System Tray
						</h3>
						<p>Runs silently in the background with easy access to settings.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title">
							<span class="text-2xl">üìú</span>
							History
						</h3>
						<p>View and copy recent transcriptions with the built-in history viewer.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="installation" class="py-20 bg-base-100">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Installation</h2>
			<div class="tabs tabs-boxed mb-6">
				<a class="tab tab-active" onclick="showInstallTab('download')">Download (Recommended)</a>
				<a class="tab" onclick="showInstallTab('source')">Build from Source</a>
			</div>
			
			<div id="install-download" class="install-content">
				<div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					<div class="card-body">
						<ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3">
							<li>Go to <a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto/releases/latest" class="link link-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Releases</a></li>
							<li>Download <code class="badge badge-neutral">oto-Setup-X.X.X.exe</code></li>
							<li>Run the installer</li>
							<li>Launch oto from Start Menu or Desktop</li>
						</ol>
						<div class="alert alert-success mt-6">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-current shrink-0 h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
							<span><strong>No .NET runtime installation required</strong> - the application is fully self-contained.</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="install-source" class="install-content hidden">
				<div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4">Build and Run</h3>
						<div class="mockup-code bg-neutral text-neutral-content">
							<pre data-prefix="$"><code>git clone https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto.git</code></pre>
							<pre data-prefix="$"><code>cd oto</code></pre>
							<pre data-prefix="$"><code>dotnet build</code></pre>
							<pre data-prefix="$"><code>dotnet run --project src/oto.App</code></pre>
						</div>
						<h3 class="card-title text-xl mb-4 mt-6">Publish Self-Contained</h3>
						<div class="mockup-code bg-neutral text-neutral-content">
							<pre data-prefix="$"><code>dotnet publish src/oto.App -c Release -r win-x64 --self-contained -o ./publish</code></pre>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="usage" class="py-20 bg-base-200">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How to Use</h2>
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<ul class="steps steps-vertical lg:steps-horizontal w-full">
					<li class="step step-primary">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-2xl mb-2">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
							<div>First Run</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">Right-click tray icon > Settings > Enter API Key</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="step step-primary">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-2xl mb-2">üéôÔ∏è</div>
							<div>Recording</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">Hold Ctrl+Alt+Space</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="step step-primary">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-2xl mb-2">‚èπÔ∏è</div>
							<div>Release</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">Release to transcribe</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="step step-primary">
						<div class="text-center">
							<div class="text-2xl mb-2">‚ú®</div>
							<div>Done!</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-1">Text pasted automatically</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="py-20 bg-base-100">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Configuration</h2>
			<div class="overflow-x-auto max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<table class="table table-zebra">
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th>Setting</th>
							<th>Description</th>
							<th>Default</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>API Key</strong></td>
							<td>Your OpenAI API key</td>
							<td><span class="badge badge-warning">required</span></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Model</strong></td>
							<td>Transcription model</td>
							<td><code>gpt-4o-mini-transcribe</code></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Hotkey</strong></td>
							<td>Key combination for recording</td>
							<td><code>Ctrl+Alt+Space</code></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Max Duration</strong></td>
							<td>Maximum recording time (seconds)</td>
							<td><code>60</code></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Language</strong></td>
							<td>Language hint (e.g., "ja", "en")</td>
							<td><code>Auto-detect</code></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Add Punctuation</strong></td>
							<td>Include punctuation in output</td>
							<td><span class="badge badge-success">Yes</span></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Preserve Newlines</strong></td>
							<td>Keep line breaks</td>
							<td><span class="badge badge-success">Yes</span></td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Restore Clipboard</strong></td>
							<td>Restore original clipboard after paste</td>
							<td><span class="badge badge-success">Yes</span></td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="py-20 bg-base-200">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Get Started Today</h2>
			<p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Download oto and start transcribing your voice with just a hotkey press.</p>
			<a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
				Download for Windows
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer class="footer items-center p-4 bg-neutral text-neutral-content">
		<aside class="items-center grid-flow-col">
			<p>Copyright ¬© 2024 - All right reserved by ikumasudo</p>
		</aside>
		<nav class="grid-flow-col gap-4 md:place-self-center md:justify-self-end">
			<a href="https://github.com/ikumasudo/oto" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-square btn-ghost">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"></path></svg>
			</a>
		</nav>
	</footer>

	<script>
		function showInstallTab(tab) {
			document.querySelectorAll('.install-content').forEach(el => el.classList.add('hidden'));
			document.querySelectorAll('.tabs a').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('tab-active'));
			document.getElementById(`install-${tab}`).classList.remove('hidden');
			event.target.classList.add('tab-active');
		}
	</script>
</Layout>
